#: ../../revision-history.rst:92
msgid ""
"The Jargon File comes alive again after a seven-year hiatus. Reorganization "
"and massive additions were by Eric S. Raymond, approved by Guy Steele. Many "
"items of UNIX, C, USENET, and microcomputer-based jargon were added at that "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Jargon Fileが7年の中断を経て再び生き返る。再編成と大規模な追加はEric S. Raymondによって行われ、Guy "
"Steeleによって承認された。UNIX、C、USENET、マイクロコンピュータベースの俗語の多くの項目がこの時に追加された。"

